name: Ananyaahhh❤️
greetingText: You must be made of copper and tellurium, because you're Cu-Te! 😘
wishText: Every time I see you, my heart whispers, ‘Tera hone laga hoon, jab se mila hoon…’ 💖 You are my ‘Suraj Hua Maddham’ moment, and the reason my heart sings ‘Tum paas aaye, yun muskuraye, tumne na jaane kya sapne dikhaye…’ 🎶
